## URL Scheme μμ 

μƒμ„±λλ” URL μμ‹:
```
upnote://x-callback-url/note/new?text=Hello%20UpNote!&title=Test%20Note
upnote://x-callback-url/note/new?text=Content&title=Title&notebook=Project&tags=tag1,tag2
upnote://x-callback-url/search?query=keyword
```

